00121 /* instruction register bit positions, see HD44780U data sheet */
00122 #define LCD_CLR       0   /* DB0: clear display         */
00123 #define LCD_HOME      1   /* DB1: return to home position   */
00124 #define LCD_ENTRY_MODE    2   /* DB2: set entry mode         */
00125 #define LCD_ENTRY_INC   1   /*   DB1: 1=increment, 0=decrement   */
00126 #define LCD_ENTRY_SHIFT   0   /*   DB2: 1=display shift on       */
00127 #define LCD_ON        3   /* DB3: turn lcd/cursor on       */
00128 #define LCD_ON_DISPLAY    2   /*   DB2: turn display on       */
00129 #define LCD_ON_CURSOR   1   /*   DB1: turn cursor on         */
00130 #define LCD_ON_BLINK    0   /*   DB0: blinking cursor ?     */
00131 #define LCD_MOVE      4   /* DB4: move cursor/display     */
00132 #define LCD_MOVE_DISP   3   /*   DB3: move display (0-> cursor) ?  */
00133 #define LCD_MOVE_RIGHT    2   /*   DB2: move right (0-> left) ?   */
00134 #define LCD_FUNCTION    5   /* DB5: function set           */
00135 #define LCD_FUNCTION_8BIT 4   /*   DB4: set 8BIT mode (0->4BIT mode) */
00136 #define LCD_FUNCTION_2LINES 3   /*   DB3: two lines (0->one line)   */
00137 #define LCD_FUNCTION_10DOTS 2   /*   DB2: 5x10 font (0->5x7 font)   */
00138 #define LCD_CGRAM     6   /* DB6: set CG RAM address       */
00139 #define LCD_DDRAM     7   /* DB7: set DD RAM address       */
00140 #define LCD_BUSY      7   /* DB7: LCD is busy         */

00142 /* set entry mode: display shift on/off, dec/inc cursor move direction */
00143 #define LCD_ENTRY_DEC   0x04  /* display shift off, dec cursor move dir */
00144 #define LCD_ENTRY_DEC_SHIFT 0x05  /* display shift on,  dec cursor move dir */
00145 #define LCD_ENTRY_INC_    0x06  /* display shift off, inc cursor move dir */
00146 #define LCD_ENTRY_INC_SHIFT 0x07  /* display shift on,  inc cursor move dir */

00152 #define LCD_DISP_ON_CURSOR  0x0E  /* display on, cursor on          */
